{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act36side", "eventName": "泰拉飯", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DT-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "海鮮拼盤", "storyInfo": "鹽風城居民的慘狀讓先西萌生了為他們做一頓豐盛的料理的想法。但此地深海教會的教士不這麼想，他看向遠處盤踞著海嗣的溶洞，做了一個決定。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibcave", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵人墜落的樣子彷彿——"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——流星。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身在深海中的人甚少看見這種奇景。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那沉迷慾望和陰謀、從不抬頭仰望的主教，更不可能知曉這等景色。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們不一樣。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當深海獵人們拼命向上游去，想從陰鬱與犧牲中掙脫時，當他們躋身海面，靜靜欣賞無邊星空時……"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵人們都在心中記錄了這些短命星辰的命運。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使如此，也會劃破黑暗。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#8", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，死吧。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 6.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_chixiaobadao"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.01, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.09, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三顆流星照亮了幽邃的通道。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主教恐懼萬分，他沒有肺，沒有聲道，這鳴響只是他的新身體用以替代慘叫的新方式。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殘垣斷壁裡，怪物將死的臃腫肉體填塞了大半個溶洞。牠原本不斷散發出奇異之美的古怪軀體因牠對死亡的畏懼而越顯僵硬。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主教死去了。他的一切都將被遺忘。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_RL2_cliffday", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情況不太妙啊。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個城市周圍沒有絲毫活物的氣息……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來在這裡很難蒐集到像樣的補給。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，有什麼發現嗎？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒什麼變化，這座城裡其他地方也都是一句話都不會說的傢伙。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們看到食物倒是會有反應，但還是不會回答我的問題。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於補給，別說讓他們分我們一些了，我甚至把身上僅剩的口糧分了一點給他們。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是，這座城市的大部分民居只能用淒涼來形容……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真難以想像，這裡的人能在這種環境下生存。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫找遍了好幾個市場，看起來都很久沒營業了。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說這裡的大部分人已經很久沒有好好吃過東西了。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫看在眼裡實在是心痛。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟著一個人一路來到海邊，本來以為能發現什麼，結果——", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_187", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_189", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_187", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝……喝……", "name": "居民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_187"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他就這樣和其他人一樣，漫無目的地在海邊遊蕩，有的時候挖一挖沙，好像沙灘上會有吃的長出來一樣……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_187", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_189", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "餓……", "name": "居民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_189"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_187", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鱗、殼，可以吃。", "name": "居民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_187"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃吧，吃吧。", "name": "居民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_187"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先西放下了手中的斧，快步走到兩人的面前，伸手打開了他們的包裹。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裡面堆放著剛從沙灘上撿拾來的鱗和殼，而且都已經輕微腐爛，發出難以忍受的腥臭味。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可兩人渾然不覺，生怕先西搶他們的，馬上就往嘴裡塞。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，這實在是……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也太淒慘了……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這裡沒什麼能幫我們的東西，我們還是儘快離開這裡吧。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的民風民俗實在是太奇怪了，人們感覺也不太友善的樣子……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是老夫的猜測。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的人很可能是長時間沒有吃過正常的食物，導致他們對周圍的一切都逐漸麻木。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這時候讓他們吃到一頓美食，或許可以讓他們恢復一點知覺。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的假的……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，你不清楚也不奇怪，長時間的食物匱乏，還有生活環境的壓縮，是會讓人一點一點麻木的。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽起來很有經驗。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果可以的話，老夫也希望讓這裡的人吃上一頓飽飯。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不管怎麼說，我們也要為自己找食物，不然的話，我們也走不了多遠，對吧，奇爾查克。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唉，說得也是。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，事先說好，補給不見了是你們在薩米亂跑搞出來的事情，所以別指望靠我！", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那當然。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遊蕩的旅行者，你們是否在尋找食物？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，你聽得懂我們的話嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了！我們——", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，瑪露希爾，其他人都聽不懂我們說話，他卻聽得懂，你不覺得奇怪嗎？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們會有所警惕也很正常。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，不用擔心，我是為了提供指引給你們而來的。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底是誰？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是一名教士，四處行走，為人們帶去大海的教誨。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們呢？你們不像是伊比利亞人，為什麼會來到這座鹽風城？", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們正在籌集旅行的補給。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來進展不太順利？", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，沒有關係，既然我們來了，就不會讓你們挨餓。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……“我們”？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#7$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我們是庇護這座城市的教會，在教會之中，人人都是兄弟手足。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "縱使你們是外來者，若願意聽從指引，便是我們的手足。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們肯定不會眼看手足受餓。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（聽起來有點詭異……）", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們能跟著他找到食物，城裡那些人也能吃到一頓正常的飯吧？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別自顧自地說出好像要入教一樣的話啊！", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，大海的恩澤無窮無盡，不會吝惜與你們分享萬億分之一。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但，只有足夠強大的人才能獲得。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我猜他的意思是，他知道哪裡有食物，但是人們不一定有命去拿。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們可以這樣理解。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不勉強你們涉險，只是——", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我們吧，我們都是有經驗的冒險者，一些危險我們還是能夠處理的。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沿著海岸線往南走，那裡有一座洞窟。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洞窟裡，有你們想要的東西。", "name": "教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_454_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibcave", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊歐斯，那個人有問題。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還聽他說的話？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的氛圍這麼奇怪，總覺得和那個人說的教會多少有點關係。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟著他所謂的“指引”，總能發現點什麼吧。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，如果有埋伏的話，奇爾查克一定能提前察覺到的吧！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，也是啦……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#12$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯？這是——", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克拉肯！好大！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊歐斯，小心！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#4$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，牠已經不會動彈了。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸！已經死掉了嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇！這麼巨大的克拉肯……那個教士果然沒有騙我們！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看這腕足，看這吸盤，看這海葵一樣的器官——這應該是牠的……頭部？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真想看看牠還活著的時候的樣子，應該跟一座塔的大小差不多，一定超級威風。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但是克拉肯很難吃呢……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是克拉肯，但似乎也是有著共同淵源的種族。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的胃開始痛了……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#22$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種來路不明的東西，絕對不能吃！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫也同意，不能吃牠。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "奇爾查克&瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海裡的生物在死後身體內可能會分泌毒素。比如螃蟹，即使死了沒有多久，也可能被病菌污染。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是真的想吃的話……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以看看裡面還有沒有活著的寄生蟲！", "name": "先西&萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊我真的是多嘴——！！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#2$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都說了這種時候最好別說話啦。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這麼龐大的生物究竟是被誰殺死的呢？想要躲開這些腕足的攻擊應該不太容易……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，萊歐斯，我聽到了什麼聲音……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪露希爾用棍子挑起一長串黏黏的、散發著螢光的東西。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……看起來有點噁心。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在白天也閃爍著螢光，好美麗……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#6$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行啦，我要丟掉它了！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#21$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真浪費……咦，丟到什麼東西上了？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1421_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#7$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1421_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "！！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——啊！！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊歐斯，注意腳下！", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——啊！這是海草？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#7$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心，萊歐斯，踩在這些海草上的感覺不太舒服。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？這麼一說……身體的確有點麻耶。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#9$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都小心一點，不要踩在這些海草上！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是按你這麼說，我們能站的地方可就不多了。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#12$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來這個洞穴裡面的這些植物，也全都是魔物嗎？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毫無疑問，我們正身處這個巨大克拉肯魔物的巢穴之中。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而正從洞穴裡湧出來的這些，都是生活在牠身邊的伴生生物。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#14$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是新鮮食材！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#20$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪露希爾，你能對著這些海草使用你的魔法嗎？放個火什麼的？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#22$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你瘋了？在這裡放火，不就等於告訴洞裡的那些怪物，我們來了嗎？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#5$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我就是這個意思。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海草是從洞窟深處蔓延過來的，追著怪物進入深處的話，只會對我們更加不利。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不如用一把火告訴牠們，我們來了。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……聽起來真的像是經過了深思熟慮之後得出的結論呢。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我們不會硬來的，你就留在外面，只要打到了足夠多的食材，我們就原路撤回。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的出了什麼事，你也可以接應我們。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嘖，隨你的便。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然還只是個孩子啊，奇爾查克。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……話說回來，你就這麼理所當然地覺得我會聽你的啊。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#22$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#22$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪露希爾看到萊歐斯的表情就知道，他的確是沒想過別的情況。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，好吧，摀住耳朵。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#14$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog"